author: tabish
msg: Adds new class ThreadPoolExecutor that is used internally by the Connection class to serialize the execution of its asynchronous exception callbacks and to garuntee that the async exception callbacks don't outlive the connection once its been closed (they were in the ThreadPool before without any way to purge them).
